---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout title="联系与更新">
  <main class="container section">
    <div class="spotlight">
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">联系页</span>
        <h1>把对外信息集中在这里</h1>
        <p>建议后续在这里补充微信、电话、预约时间、常见问题和服务说明。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">GitHub 更新</span>
        <h2>内容更新方式</h2>
        <p>把站点推到 GitHub 后，修改 Markdown 或页面文件并提交，即可通过 Actions 自动部署。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>
